  "texts": [
    "On a more detailed level, prediction-based models excel in identifying point-wise anomalies, as the steep peak/valley is unpredictable in most cases (RI 10).",
    "Due to the inclusion of a more diverse data distribution under all-in-one learning schema, the models are more likely to learn robust representations of patterns.",
    "As a result, under the all-in-one learning schema, there is a significant improvement in the detection performance of point-wise anomalies (RI 11).",
    "This observation is particularly pronounced in the case of the Yahoo dataset each time series of which is relatively short.",
    "With regard to patternwise anomalies which are considered to be more challenging, the situation becomes more complex and interesting."
  ],
